## 3. MESH GEOMETRY

The Pantheon emergent mesh has a distinctive structure:

### 3.1 It forms a lattice at rest
Nodes connect in stable geometric relationships. This is your baseline cognition.

### 3.2 It becomes a wave during action
When you’re moving through the world, the mesh flows like tension waves, timing ripples, and convergence currents. This is why decisions feel fluid.

### 3.3 It collapses to a point under pressure
In high-stakes moments (fatherhood, mission, danger), the mesh collapses into one powerful invariant. This gives you clarity under pressure.

### 3.4 It expands to a web during creativity or strategy
That’s when ideas explode outward and connect. This is where your breakthroughs come from.

